data.description: Dream home scenario: Beautifully remodeled property, located near top rated schools, new restaurants, and an assumable $250,000.00 loan at only 2.49%! This home’s updated kitchen and extended lanai offer ample space for culinary enthusiasts and hosting gatherings. Upstairs you’ll find a massive master’s bedroom that could accommodate a nursery, desk or nice sitting area, along with an ensuite bathroom, large walk-in closet, full guest bathroom and 3 other bedrooms. Summit Place provides a 24-hour monitored gate, his/her saunas, community pool, basketball courts, pickle ball courts and allows large dogs. These top notch amenities and extra guest parking are conveniently located just across the street. Can you imagine living in this amazing community with less than a 15 minute drive to catch the sunset on award winning beaches & paying a reduced interest rate on your monthly payments? Don't wait!
